text: mariyu allah mariyu ayana sandesaharudu, oka visayanlo nirnayam tisukunnappudu, visvasincina purusuniki gani leka visvasincina striki gani a visayanlo maroka nirnayam tisukune hakku ledu. Mariyu evadaite allah mariyu ayana sandesaharuniki avidheyudavutado, vastavanga, atadu spastamaina margabhrastatvanlo padi unnatle
